quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,55,"Nta cyaha kuri bo (abagore b’intumwa, baramutse batikwije) imbere ya ba se, abahungu babo, basaza babo, abahungu ba basaza babo, abahungu ba bakuru babo cyangwa barumuna babo, abagore bagenzi babo cyangwa abaja babo. Kandi mutinye Allah. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umuhamya uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  33,56,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah ahundagaza impuhwe ze ku Muhanuzi (Muhamadi) ndetse n’Abamalayika bakazimusabira. Yemwe abemeye! Nimumusabire impuhwe munamwifurize amahoro"
  33,57,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi barakaza Allah (bamubangikanya) bakanabuza amahoro Intumwa ye, Allah yarabavumye hano ku isi ndetse no ku mperuka, kandi yabateganyirije ibihano bisuzuguza"
  33,58,"Na babandi babuza amahoro abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi nta kibi bakoze, rwose baba bikoreye ikinyoma n’icyaha kigaragara"
  33,59,"Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Bwira abagore bawe, abakobwa bawe n’abagore b’abemeramana (bambare) imyambaro yabo bikwije; ibyo ni byo bizatuma bamenyekana (nk’abagore biyubashye), bityo ntibasagarirwe. Kandi Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  33,60,"Indyarya n’abafite uburwayi mu mitima yabo (bwo kurarikira ubusambanyi) ndetse n’abakwirakwiza ibihuha mu mujyi wa Madina, nibatabireka, rwose tuzagushishikariza kubatera, hanyuma ntibazongere kuwuturanamo nawe usibye igihe gito"
  33,61,(Abo) ni ibivume. Aho bazasangwa hose bazafatwe maze bicwe
  33,62,Uwo ni umugenzo wa Allah kuri babandi (indyarya) babayeho mbere. Kandi ntuzigera ubona icyasimbura umugenzo wa Allah